<link>https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=HEWIT-NG;4b303385.1404</link>   <description> Dear All,<br><br>A very brief note to let you all know that, in line with the need for the<br>PSBA network to meet PSN accreditation standards, we have upgraded our<br>netsight monitoring system to make use of SNMP v3.<br><br>From your perspectives, you should see no difference in terms of your use<br>of netsight and if you do experience any issues please do not hesitate to<br>get in touch with us via the service desk: service@ja.net [...]    </description> <item rdf:about="https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=HEWIT-NG;89d662df.1404">   <title>Interim Arrangements for Janet Customer Engagement </title>   <link>https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=HEWIT-NG;89d662df.1404</link>   <description> Dear All,<br><br>As I'm sure you are aware, I will be leaving Janet later this month to<br>take up a position in Research, Partnerships and Innovation at Liverpool<br>University. Thank you for the openness shown by all of the community<br>during my time working in Wales with Janet.<br><br>The recruitment of my replacement is well progressed and I understand that<br>a number of strong candidates applied for the position. I believe that the<br>aim is to recruit over the coming month with the new Customer Engagement<br>Manager starting after their relevant notice period. [...]    </description>   <dc:date>2014-04-07T08:23:57+00:00</dc:date>   <dc:creator>Paul Bevan</dc:creator>   <dc:identifier>https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=HEWIT-NG;89d662df.1404</dc:identifier> </item>   </rdf:RDF>
